    <item>
      <title>《泰晤士报》对自闭症治疗诊所调查的 5 个要点</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/23/health/autisim-clinics-investigation.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[快速发展的行业经常对患有自闭症的幼儿开出过多的治疗处方，这些儿童每周在这些设施中待的时间多达 40 个小时。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/23/health/autisim-clinics-investigation.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 09:00:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>午睡时间短，时间长：自闭症诊所如何从学龄前儿童身上榨取医疗补助资金</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/23/health/autism-therapy-clinics.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该行业发展迅速，导致国家预算紧张。对财务的关注导致了超额计费、欺诈甚至伤害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/23/health/autism-therapy-clinics.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 09:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曾经是特朗普对抗伊朗的副驾驶，内塔尼亚胡现在只是过客</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/23/world/middleeast/israel-trump-iran.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为战争伙伴，以色列在很大程度上被排除在和平谈判之外，这对其总理来说是一个令人羞愧的挫折，也给该国带来了巨大的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/23/world/middleeast/israel-trump-iran.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 05:43:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普权衡对伊朗实施新打击的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/22/us/politics/trump-iran-targets.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果他决定发动袭击，就不乏目标：未受影响的能源设施、伊斯法罕地下深处的核储存设施以及似乎已被挖出来的导弹基地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/22/us/politics/trump-iran-targets.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 02:44:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普政府表示绿卡申请者必须离开美国才能申请</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/22/us/politics/green-card-changes-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这一变化可能会影响数十万人。移民律师表示，由于配偶或亲属等待申请决定，这还可能导致更多的家庭离散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/22/us/politics/green-card-changes-trump.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 01:14:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
